title: The Underground Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A full-service bakery in the heart of Dennis Village, Cape Cod, serving cappuccino, pastries, candies, fresh baked bread. Will make vegan baked good with advance request. Offers soy milk, almond milk made in-house, vegan sandwiches and soups, and more.
